content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 46.11 - Herd tests

State Regulations

Cattle herd tests shall include all animals over nine
months of age except steers, spayed heifers, and officially vaccinated animals
less than 20 months of age. Notes
